dynamic linkers looking for a dyanmic libarary 
1. directories listed in the 'LD_LIBRARY_PATH'
2. directories listed in the executable's 'rpath'
3. directories on the system search path, which consists of the entries in /etc/ld.so.conf plus /lib and /user/lib

// reconfigure dynamic linker run-time bindings
sudo ldconfig


